<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٧-<span style="color:#006d98"> قَالَ:</span> وَسَمِعْتُ يَحْيَى يَقُولُ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>اجْعَلُوا قُلُوبَكُمْ رِبَاطًا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَالصِّدْقَ سِلاحًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَمَنْ شَغَلَكُمْ عَنِ اللَّهِ فَهُوَ عدوٌ لكم؛ فعلى هذا فقاتلوا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>